column1: Abandonment Rate (after 30 seconds):  Less than or equal to 8% monthly and a rolling 12 month average of less than or equal to 4%.
CSAT: Equal to or than than 64% on a monthly basis and a rolling 12 month average that is equal to or higher than 71%.
DSAT: Equal to or less than 23% on a monthly basis and a rolling 12 month average that is equal to or less than 18%.
